<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="16" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="3.[811,1457,1588,2028]" box="[813,1030,1588,1614]" pageId="3" pageNumber="16">LECTOTYPIFICATION</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[811,1457,1588,2028]" pageId="3" pageNumber="16">
In the protologue of 
<taxonomicName box="[1028,1234,1619,1645]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gesneriaceae" genus="Lysionotus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="3" pageNumber="16" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pubescens">
<emphasis box="[1028,1234,1619,1645]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="16">Lysionotus pubescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="CLARKE C. B." box="[1248,1398,1619,1645]" firstAuthor="Clarke" journalOrPublisher="Journal of the Linnean Society, Botany" pageId="3" pageNumber="16" pagination="1 - 107" part="25" refId="ref2417" refString="CLARKE C. B. 1889. - On the plants of Kohima and Muneypore. Journal of the Linnean Society, Botany 25: 1 - 107. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1095 - 8339.1889. tb 00793. x" title="On the plants of Kohima and Muneypore" type="journal article" year="1889">Clarke (1889)</bibRefCitation>
cited “North Muneypore [
<collectingRegion box="[1040,1145,1650,1677]" country="India" name="Manipur" pageId="3" pageNumber="16">Manipur</collectingRegion>
], alt. 
<quantity box="[1208,1313,1651,1678]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.6764" pageId="3" pageNumber="16" unit="ft" value="5500.0">5500 feet</quantity>
[n. 41283]” along with an illustration (
<bibRefCitation author="CLARKE C. B." box="[1097,1230,1683,1709]" firstAuthor="Clarke" journalOrPublisher="Journal of the Linnean Society, Botany" pageId="3" pageNumber="16" pagination="1 - 107" part="25" refId="ref2417" refString="CLARKE C. B. 1889. - On the plants of Kohima and Muneypore. Journal of the Linnean Society, Botany 25: 1 - 107. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1095 - 8339.1889. tb 00793. x" title="On the plants of Kohima and Muneypore" type="journal article" year="1889">Clarke 1889</bibRefCitation>
: pl. 23) which is also original material according to Art 9.4. (
<bibRefCitation author="TURLAND N. J. &amp; WIERSEMA J. H. &amp; BARRIE F. R. &amp; GREUTER W. &amp; HAWKSWORTH D. L. &amp; HERENDEEN P. S. &amp; KNAPP S. &amp; KUSBER W. - H. &amp; LI D. - Z. &amp; MARHOLD K. &amp; MAY T. W. &amp; MCNEILL J. &amp; MONRO A. M. &amp; PRADO J. &amp; PRICE M. J. &amp; SMITH G. F." bookContentInfo="254 p." box="[1235,1439,1714,1741]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Turland" journalOrPublisher="Koeltz Botanical Books, Glashutten" pageId="3" pageNumber="16" refId="ref2875" refString="TURLAND N. J., WIERSEMA J. H., BARRIE F. R., GREUTER W., HAWKSWORTH D. L., HERENDEEN P. S., KNAPP S., KUSBER W. - H., LI D. - Z., MARHOLD K., MAY T. W., MCNEILL J., MONRO A. M., PRADO J., PRICE M. J. &amp; SMITH G. F. (eds) 2018. - International Code of Nomenclature for Algae, Fungi, and Plants (Shenzhen Code) adopted by the Nineteenth International Botanical Congress, Shenzhen, China, July 2017. Regnum Vegetabile 159. Koeltz Botanical Books, Glashutten, 254 p. https: // doi. org / 10.12705 / code. 2018" title="International Code of Nomenclature for Algae, Fungi, and Plants (Shenzhen Code) adopted by the Nineteenth International Botanical Congress, Shenzhen, China, July 2017" type="book" year="2018">
Turland 
<emphasis box="[1327,1377,1714,1740]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="16">et al.</emphasis>
2018
</bibRefCitation>
), and since Clarke omitted to explicitly state a 
<typeStatus box="[1329,1430,1746,1772]" pageId="3" pageNumber="16">holotype</typeStatus>
, a lectotypification is necessary (Art. 9.3., 
<bibRefCitation author="TURLAND N. J. &amp; WIERSEMA J. H. &amp; BARRIE F. R. &amp; GREUTER W. &amp; HAWKSWORTH D. L. &amp; HERENDEEN P. S. &amp; KNAPP S. &amp; KUSBER W. - H. &amp; LI D. - Z. &amp; MARHOLD K. &amp; MAY T. W. &amp; MCNEILL J. &amp; MONRO A. M. &amp; PRADO J. &amp; PRICE M. J. &amp; SMITH G. F." bookContentInfo="254 p." box="[1234,1439,1778,1804]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Turland" journalOrPublisher="Koeltz Botanical Books, Glashutten" pageId="3" pageNumber="16" refId="ref2875" refString="TURLAND N. J., WIERSEMA J. H., BARRIE F. R., GREUTER W., HAWKSWORTH D. L., HERENDEEN P. S., KNAPP S., KUSBER W. - H., LI D. - Z., MARHOLD K., MAY T. W., MCNEILL J., MONRO A. M., PRADO J., PRICE M. J. &amp; SMITH G. F. (eds) 2018. - International Code of Nomenclature for Algae, Fungi, and Plants (Shenzhen Code) adopted by the Nineteenth International Botanical Congress, Shenzhen, China, July 2017. Regnum Vegetabile 159. Koeltz Botanical Books, Glashutten, 254 p. https: // doi. org / 10.12705 / code. 2018" title="International Code of Nomenclature for Algae, Fungi, and Plants (Shenzhen Code) adopted by the Nineteenth International Botanical Congress, Shenzhen, China, July 2017" type="book" year="2018">
Turland 
<emphasis box="[1326,1377,1778,1804]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="16">et al.</emphasis>
2018
</bibRefCitation>
). We have traced three relevant herbarium sheets at K with the collection numbers 41283A (K000831989), 41283D (K000831990) and 41283E (K000831991). All specimens have mature capsules and detailed field labels. Among them, K000831989 bears four fruiting branches and an annotation by Clarke:“shrub 
<quantity box="[995,1073,1970,1996]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.1336" metricValueMax="2.4384" metricValueMin="1.8288" pageId="3" pageNumber="16" unit="ft" value="7.0" valueMax="8.0" valueMin="6.0">6-8 feet</quantity>
long, semi pendent, much branched, 
<taxonomicName authority="Akhil &amp; Möller &amp; Nampy, 2022" authorityName="Akhil &amp; Möller &amp; Nampy" authorityYear="2022" box="[811,1018,2001,2027]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gesneriaceae" genus="Lysionotus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="3" pageNumber="16" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pubescens" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[811,1018,2001,2027]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="16">Lysionotus pubescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1025,1107,2002,2028]" pageId="3" pageNumber="16" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
”, is selected here as the 
<typeStatus box="[1351,1452,2001,2027]" pageId="3" pageNumber="16">lectotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
